<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body,
    h1,
    h2,
    h3,
    h4,
    p {
      margin: 0px;
      padding: 0px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Montserrat", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
    }

    #container {
      margin: 0px auto;
      height: auto;
      border: solid 0.5px #497B62;
      border-radius: 20px 0px 20px 20px;
      max-width: 800px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    #top-img {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px 0px 20px 0px;
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 45px;
    }

    #logo-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }


    #content {
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0px 25px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px auto;
    }

    #content h2 {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 23px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #497B62;
    }

    #content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: auto;
      color: #497B62;
      opacity: 90%;
    }

    #content p b a,
    #steps li b a {
      color: #497B62;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    #steps {
      margin: 25px auto;
      text-align: left;
      width: 80%;
      color: #497B62;
    }

    #steps h3 {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #497B62;
      text-align: center;
    }

    #steps ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      list-style: none;
    }

    #steps li {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      width: auto;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      border: solid 2px #D2ECDF;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 25px;
    }

    #steps li>span {
      font-size: 40px;
      background-color: #D2ECDF;
      color: #497B62;
      font-weight: bolder;
      display: block;
      line-height: 1.8;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 100%;
      margin: auto;
      border: solid #497B62 4px;
    }

    #steps li p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin: 15px auto;
    }
  #steps li p #step_link {
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    #link {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #D2ECDF;
      font-size: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 40px;
      padding: 5px 80px;
      border-radius: 45px;
      background-color: #497B62;
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
      margin: auto;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    footer #links {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #D2ECDF;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #497B62;
      padding: 15px 0px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-radius: 0px 0px 20px 20px;
    }

    footer #links>a {
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #497B62;
      margin: 0px 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    /* media query */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      #container {
        border-radius: 0;
      }

      #content h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      #content p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      #steps {
        width: 100%;
      }

      #steps h3 {
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      #steps li p {
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      #link {
        font-size: 14px;
        padding: 8px 50px;
        line-height: 30px;
      }

      footer #links>a {
        display: block;
        margin: 10px auto;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="container">
    <img id="top-img" src="cid:icon@cid" width="100%">
    <!-- Logo -->
    <div id="logo-container">
      <img src="cid:logo@cid" alt="Magnify Logo" width="220" />
    </div>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div id="content">
      <h2>Hello, {{name}}</h2>
      <p>
        Your account has been created successfully on <b>{{company}}</b>.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can now login using your registered email: <b>{{email}}</b>.
      </p>
      <!-- register steps -->
      <div id="steps">
        <h3>Next steps to complete your account setup:</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <span>1</span>
            <p>Access your Magnify account through the login page below,
              <br> using your email: <b>{{email}}</b> and the default password: <b>User1234</b>
              . <a href={{loginLink}} id="link">Login page</a>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>2</span>
            <p>Verify your account by clicking
              <span id="step_link">Send
                verification link
              </span>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>3</span>
            <p>
              You will receive a confirmation message on your email, then click on 
              <span id="step_link">Verify my account</span>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>4</span>
            <p>After confirming the account, it will take you to the create password page. Create a new password that
              meets
              the conditions, then click on <span id="step_link">Set new
                password</span></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>5</span>
            <p>After resetting a new password, you will be taken to the login page. Register with your email and new
              password and start exploring Magnify and enjoy our features.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <div id="links">
        <a href="">Thanks, Magnify</a>
        <a href="https://magnify-vt.com/contact/">Need help? <b>Contact us</b></a>
        <a href="https://magnify-vt.com/privacy-policy/"><b>Privacy policy</b></a>
      </div>
      <p>
        Â© {{year}} {{company}}. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>

</html>